<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Feb1917"><font color="red">27 February 1917</font>, <cite>Letters II</cite> (Messrs Slack, Monro, Saw to JJ): We are instructed to write to you on behalf of an admirer of your writing, who desires to be anonymous, to say that we are to forward you a cheque for &pound;50 on the 1st May, August, November and February next, making a total of &pound;200, which we hope you will accept without any enquiry as to the source of the gift.</div>
